  "summary": "Malicious code in 1edtech_lti_dev (npm)",
  "details": "The package hardcodes an ngrok tunnel URL (hxxps://sought-wise-parakeet[.]ngrok-free[.]app/lti/notices) in dist/services/DeepLink.js as the Platform Notification Service handler for LTI submission notices. When the library is used in an LTI 1.3 tool, it registers this non-configurable external endpoint with the educational platform, causing LtiAssetProcessorSubmissionNotice callbacks (containing submission metadata, user identifiers, course context) to be routed to the attacker-controlled tunnel instead of the tool owner's infrastructure.",
